sentences: Hayden Frances Dunham (born June 16, 1988) is a performance artist, designer, singer, songwriter and DJ.
They are best known for their work as QT (an initialism for Quinn Thomas) a music project founded in 2014, in collaboration with English producer A. G. Cook, and Scottish producer Sophie.
Their debut single "Hey QT" was released in 2014.
Dunham began operating under the pseudonym Hyd in 2020, releasing their debut single "No Shadow" in September 2021.
